---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Leadership Philosophy | Sriman Tirupathy Eshwarappa"
  description="Details on Sriman's experience leading architects, developers, and cross-functional teams across various engagements."
>
  <article class="pt-32 pb-24">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
      
      <!-- Header -->
      <header class="mb-16">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 mb-6 text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[0.2em] text-accent uppercase bg-accent/5 rounded-full border border-accent/10">
          People & Delivery
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tighter mb-6">
          Leadership & Team Building
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          I build high-performing engineering cultures by focusing on mentorship, structured quality gates, and automated delivery models. My leadership ensures that technical excellence translates directly into business velocity. Below are highlights of the teams I have had the privilege to lead across different engagements.
        </p>
      </header>

      <!-- Content Sections -->
      <div class="space-y-12">
        
        <!-- Present Engagement -->
        <section class="glass p-8 md:p-12 rounded-3xl border-l-4 border-l-accent hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow bg-white/50 border border-slate-200">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center text-accent">
               <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight">Publicis Sapient</h2>
              <div class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500 font-bold mt-1">Enterprise Architecture & Delivery</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
            In my current role, I am responsible for driving the technical vision and execution of mission-critical integration platforms. I directly lead a highly specialized, senior engineering group comprising:
          </p>
          <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
             <li class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-100">
                <div class="text-accent"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="12 2 2 7 12 12 22 7 12 2"></polygon><polyline points="2 17 12 22 22 17"></polyline><polyline points="2 12 12 17 22 12"></polyline></svg></div>
                <div class="font-bold text-slate-900">4 Integration Architects</div>
             </li>
             <li class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-100">
                <div class="text-accent"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"></polyline><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"></polyline></svg></div>
                <div class="font-bold text-slate-900">10 Senior Developers</div>
             </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Previous Engagement -->
        <section class="glass p-8 md:p-12 rounded-3xl hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow bg-white/50 border border-slate-200 relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute right-0 top-0 w-32 h-32 bg-accent/5 rounded-bl-[100px] -z-10"></div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-600">
               <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="18" cy="18" r="3"></circle><circle cx="6" cy="6" r="3"></circle><path d="M13 6h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v7"></path><line x1="6" y1="9" x2="6" y2="21"></line></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight">Red Sea Global</h2>
              <div class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500 font-bold mt-1">Cross-Functional Delivery</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Prior to my current role, I managed a diverse, cross-functional delivery team. Guiding a multidisciplinary team required establishing unified DevOps pipelines, standardized communication protocols, and maintaining a cohesive architectural vision across:
          </p>
          <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
             <li class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-100">
                <div class="text-accent"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"></circle></svg></div>
                <div class="font-bold text-slate-900">1 Platform Sr. Dev</div>
             </li>
             <li class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-100">
                <div class="text-accent"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"></polyline><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"></polyline></svg></div>
                <div class="font-bold text-slate-900">4 Integration Devs</div>
             </li>
             <li class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-100">
                <div class="text-accent"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"></line><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"></line></svg></div>
                <div class="font-bold text-slate-900">1 DevOps Sr. Dev</div>
             </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Virtusa -->
        <section class="glass p-8 md:p-12 rounded-3xl hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow bg-white/50 border border-slate-200 relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute right-0 top-0 w-32 h-32 bg-accent/5 rounded-bl-[100px] -z-10"></div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-600">
               <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"></polyline></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight">Virtusa</h2>
              <div class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500 font-bold mt-1">Foundational Team Leadership</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
            During my tenure at Virtusa, I was entrusted with leading a foundational engineering team. This experience solidified my core management philosophy of fostering individual contributor growth while ensuring strict alignment with overarching project milestones across:
          </p>
          <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
             <li class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-100">
                <div class="text-accent"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="12 2 2 7 12 12 22 7 12 2"></polygon><polyline points="2 17 12 22 22 17"></polyline><polyline points="2 12 12 17 22 12"></polyline></svg></div>
                <div class="font-bold text-slate-900">2 Architects</div>
             </li>
             <li class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-100">
                <div class="text-accent"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path></svg></div>
                <div class="font-bold text-slate-900">4 Senior Devs</div>
             </li>
             <li class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-100">
                <div class="text-accent"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"></circle></svg></div>
                <div class="font-bold text-slate-900">4 Junior Devs</div>
             </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

      </div>
      
      <!-- Call to Action -->
      <div class="mt-16 text-center lg:text-left">
         <a href="/#leadership" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-500 hover:text-accent font-bold text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest transition-colors mb-8">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="19" y1="12" x2="5" y2="12"></line><polyline points="12 19 5 12 12 5"></polyline></svg>
            Back to Home
         </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
